{"type": "article", "id": 11913, "title": "星际迷航通讯器", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-10T11:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000108k67cFUtbCr0anD39.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t星际迷们，现在又有好消息了，Wand 公司做了一个星际迷航通讯器。为了保证细节上相符采用结构化轻3D扫描技术。它可以进行通话，也可以瞬间变身蓝牙播放器，底部的磁性支架可以对通讯器进行无线充电，甚至还配有一个外壳，看上去非常的酷炫。这是<a href=\"http://www.thewandcompany.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Wand 公司的主页</a>，点击可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135900Ai6bTyE7rSBaqX28.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"846\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.03422983\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135900Ug8Fv2wBOPkbeztp.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1272\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.55501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135901BnW73tsuHFkE0KZO.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"1152\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.40831296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135901DRUP8ZdxKSFfJsLH.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"641\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78361858\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}